### List users (admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users?page=1&pageSize=10&search=
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### List users (admin filtered by branchCode)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users?page=1&pageSize=10&search=&branchCode=02
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### List users (manager, only own branch)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{managerJwt}}

### List users (seller - forbidden)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{sellerJwt}}

### Create user (admin)
POST https://cotizador-core-a7900f43ba87.herokuapp.com/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Erick",
  "lastName": "Ramirez",
  "username": "eeramirez",
  "email": "eeramirez@tuvansa.com.mx",
  "password": "Ag7348pp**",
  "role": "SELLER",
  "branchCode": "02",
  "phone": "8119999999",
  "erpUserCode": "ERP-SELLER-001"
}

### Create user (manager, own branch only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{managerJwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Branch",
  "lastName": "Seller",
  "username": "branchseller",
  "email": "branch.seller@tuvansa.com",
  "password": "Tuvansa123!",
  "role": "SELLER",
  "branchCode": "02"
}

### Update user (admin/manager)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/REPLACE_USER_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Updated",
  "lastName": "User",
  "username": "updated.user",
  "email": "updated.user@tuvansa.com",
  "role": "SELLER",
  "branchCode": "02",
  "phone": "8119999999",
  "erpUserCode": "ERP-SELLER-001"
}

### Deactivate user (admin only)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/REPLACE_USER_ID/deactivate
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
